wikipedia_page.main: Chester Mojay-Sinclare (born c. 1989) is a British entrepreneur. He is the founder of social enterprise Enthuse and Spudnik, the not-for-profit educational space project.

response: The company was founded by Chester Mojay-Sinclare in 2009, and its flagship online fundraising service Charity Checkout was launched in 2011. Mojay-Sinclare was still a student when the company was launched.
